Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Zeichnung "Simson mit den Löwen" "

-  Draft text "Rubens und der Löwe (zu einer Zeichnung in Amsterdam)" by Evers
- Photos of paintings, drawings, sculptures and engravings about the lion hunt
- Correspondence with Ladendorf dated 1963

- Booklet: "Bulletin van het Rijksmuseum", n.3, 1955
- Extracts from different publications
- Bibliographic references
- Library loan form

- Correspondence with H. Gerson dated 1963
